  Day 18

  Methods : Function

     public static void main(String[] args){

     }

     declaring a method:

     Access-Modifier    Specifier    Return Type   Method Name (Parameters){

     }

     Access modifiers: public, protected, default , private

     Specifier: static, final, abstract, synchronised

     Return Type: void, Any Data Type

     Method Name: can be anything

     parameters: any data types

     Custom Methods
     1. void methods
     2. void methods with arguments/parameters
     3. return methods
     4. return with arguments
     5. method overloading

